Carbonite Office
Plans start at just $269.99/year
 
Backs up unlimited computers
Carbonite Office plans cover every computer. You can upgrade your plan to include one or more servers - and add storage space as you need it.
Makes remote management easy
It's simple to install and maintain Carbonite cloud or hybrid backup across multiple workstations - from one intuitive, user-friendly dashboard.
Supports regulatory compliance
Every Carbonite Office plan supports HIPAA, FERPA, and GLBA compliance.




Carbonite Home
Plans start at just $59.99/year
 
Offers unlimited storage
Carbonite Home backs up everything on your computer - including photos, videos and music. You never have to worry about storage space.
Operates automatically
After an easy initial setup - just install Carbonite on your computer - it backs up your digital files automatically. You never have to lift a finger.
Allows access from anywhere
Your backup is available from any web browser - recover one file or all of them in just a few clicks.















