Cloud Backup
You know your data is safe with Carbonite
Carbonite gives you powerful protection against human error, hardware failures, ransomware and all the other major reasons why businesses lose data.

Automatic cloud backup for computers, external hard drives, and physical or virtual servers
Easy to install, configure and restore
Access files from anywhere via web-based dashboard
Advanced end-to-end encryption for data at rest and in-flight
Award-winning business support 7 days/week

Free TrialLearn More















 


Cloud + On-Site Backup
Introducing E2 hybrid backup
Protect all the data at your small business both on-site and in the cloud with powerful hybrid backup powered by EVault.

Combines the speed of on-site recovery with the added security of cloud backup
Simple pricing is based on the size of your data footprint, including retention
Includes hardware, software and a year of version history in the cloud
Supports all popular operating systems and applications, including virtualized networks
Browser-based portal lets you log in and recover data remotely

Learn More















Carbonite solutions are built for business
Early in their startup phase, Boston Common Coffee Company invested in a Carbonite subscription. When their computer hard drive crashed unexpectedly, all they had to do was log into their Carbonite account, press a button, and everything started transferring over to a new computer. View this short video to hear why this business owner says his Carbonite subscription is invaluable.
Read more customer stories








Boston Common Coffee Company owner says that his Carbonite subscription is invaluable.
